  "summary": "A reusable Docusaurus 3.8.1 template with TypeScript, designed for professional documentation sites. Features advanced theming, commenting, and project badging systems, with automated pre-build scripts for markdown and navbar generation. Includes dynamic theme switching, GitHub integration, and support for Docker-based workflows. Ideal for maintainable, scalable, and visually appealing documentation projects.",
